Microsoft 365 & Infrastructure Management Tools
Copyright 2025 Microsoft 365 & Infrastructure Management Tools

This product includes software developed for Microsoft 365 and infrastructure management automation.

This project contains PowerShell scripts for:
- Active Directory management
- Microsoft 365 administration (Exchange Online, Azure AD, Intune)
- Azure resource management
- Security and compliance automation
- Grafana monitoring integration

