This project uses the following Microsoft PowerShell modules:
- Microsoft.Graph (https://github.com/microsoftgraph/msgraph-sdk-powershell)
- ExchangeOnlineManagement (https://www.powershellgallery.com/packages/ExchangeOnlineManagement)
- Az PowerShell (https://github.com/Azure/azure-powershell)
- PnP.PowerShell (https://github.com/pnp/powershell)
- Microsoft.PowerShell.SecretManagement
- Microsoft.PowerShell.SecretStore
- ActiveDirectory

Each module is subject to its own license terms.

